## Nangula kalemba Mark tasuntinkenye ilembo tulelolekeshapo na malembo yafumineko, 
## cilifye icaololoka ukutila Yesu ali ne milimo iyafula icungulo bushiku iya kundapa nokutamfya ingulu ngefyo twingamona ukufuma mu versi 21-34.
