## Ukwenda mu ntampulo sha bashifwe.
## Isaac atendeka ukwimbulula ifishima ifyashile wishi, no kufinika amashina ayo wishi afinike. 
## Aya yali matontonkanyo ayasuma kuli Isaac ukwimbulula ifishima, ukucila ukwimba ifipya, pantu ifipya amenshi tayabuta bwangu pakuti tuyabomfye. 
## Lelo kwena ukwimbulula ifyashikilwemo amabwe no kupwa imyaka iingi te cintu cayanguka iyoo.
## Nga twamona mwibuku lya Shamfumu tusangamo ifyo limo limo abana balecita ifyo abafyashi balecita. 
## Hisekia abukulwile imipepele isuma yakwa wishi Dabidi no konaula ifilubi fyonse ifyali mu musumba. 
## Na ifwe tulingile ukunwisha abantu amenshi ya mweo ayali na maka ya kubapwisha icilaka, ifyo abafyashi besu bacitile. 
