## Eco mulimo wesu ukulungika imipepele yesu iyaonaike akale, pakuti tupusushe imyeo ya bantu.
## Sambilileni ku fyakale, citeni ifintu ifipya!
## Apa twamona ifyo ababomfi bakwa Isaac baimbile ifishima fimbi ifipya, twamona ifyo ababomfi bakwa Isaac balundilepo ifishima fimbi ifipya pa fyakale. 
## Eco tuli nokubomfya ulubuuto lwa fintu fyakale ku kuletelamo ifipya.
## Tulingile ukutontonkanya pa kulundapo te kwikalafye ne fishima fyakale.
